1
00:00:42,850 --> 00:00:48,540
♪Flower petals have fallen,
piling as high as mortal mercilessness♪

2
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:55,410
♪Gone with the wind,
as if it has never existed♪

3
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:59,960
♪I ask for more time♪

4
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,290
♪To rewrite our stories♪

5
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:09,650
♪We travel together in joys and woes♪

6
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:16,470
♪Blood bathes this entangled destiny♪

7
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:23,260
♪For the next reunion
in the troubled times♪

8
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,380
♪We tread a treacherous path♪

9
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,640
♪To find each other♪

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:37,600
♪Wars and bleakness,
the bright moon shines upon the city♪

11
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,930
♪I will offer my bravery♪

12
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:44,380
♪Fighting relentlessly♪

13
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:47,630
♪All for no regrets♪

14
00:01:47,708 --> 00:01:51,348
♪In this life-and-death battle,
I will not back down♪

15
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:54,910
♪Withstand enduring time♪

16
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:58,130
♪Someone at the end of the world
never leaves♪

17
00:01:58,270 --> 00:02:05,210
♪I brave the grim haze
to be with you once again♪

18
00:02:05,210 --> 00:02:10,950
=Love of Nirvana=
(Based on Xiao Lou's novel of the same name)

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,180
=Episode 22=

20
00:02:18,090 --> 00:02:18,690
Let's split up.

21
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:19,530
Sure.

22
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,780
Elder Hong,

23
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,880
I remember you.

24
00:03:05,350 --> 00:03:06,030
Who are you?

25
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:09,680
As long as the jade hairpin
is in my hand,

26
00:03:09,736 --> 00:03:12,200
you can forget about
securing the position of city lord.

27
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:20,160
Stop chasing.

28
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:21,160
Father!

29
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:22,910
This is a serious matter,

30
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,340
we need to plan carefully.

31
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:30,350
Elder Hong,

32
00:03:30,530 --> 00:03:32,340
did you find out that man's identity

33
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:34,220
when you confronted him?

34
00:03:35,290 --> 00:03:36,410
All I know is

35
00:03:37,070 --> 00:03:39,910
he admitted that
he has the jade hairpin.

36
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,400
The jade hairpin has been missing

37
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,570
ever since the death of Xiao Haitian.

38
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,960
That man has been defending
Xiao Haitian today.

39
00:03:56,090 --> 00:03:57,160
Could he be

40
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:58,970
Xiao Wuxia?

41
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,970
The jade hairpin indeed

42
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:07,940
went missing along with

43
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,720
the siblings
of the Xiao family those days.

44
00:04:13,192 --> 00:04:14,400
If he is really Xiao Wuxia,

45
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,420
I will definitely confront him.

46
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:20,770
Xiao Wuxia's fate has been unknown
for many years.

47
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,180
If that's really him,

48
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:23,920
there is something fishy

49
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,570
about his sudden appearance.

50
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:27,210
Could it be

51
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:30,240
that he's here to compete
for the position of city lord?

52
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,300
How dare he.

53
00:04:31,650 --> 00:04:32,980
All the incidents in Yueluo

54
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:34,330
are caused by the Xiao family,

55
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:36,536
yet he has the nerve
to claim himself to be the city lord?

56
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,150
Even if he wants to fight for it,

57
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:40,040
who in this city recognizes him?

58
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,040
What do you intend to do?

59
00:04:51,650 --> 00:04:53,180
According to Yueluo tribe's teachings,

60
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,130
to be the city lord,

61
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:56,936
indeed, one has to possess
the jade hairpin.

62
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:57,710
At present,

63
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,180
since we have clues
about the jade hairpin,

64
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,210
isn't this a golden opportunity

65
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:03,240
to unite Yueluo tribe?

66
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,710
If he is really Xiao Wuxia,

67
00:05:05,816 --> 00:05:07,860
not only can we provide
an explanation to the tribe,

68
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:09,910
but we can also establish
our authority and prestige.

69
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:13,480
Well,

70
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:15,740
Elder Li, you are saying...

71
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,270
Although I came first

72
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,070
in today's election,

73
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:25,190
having a vote-based competition
was a last resort,

74
00:05:25,330 --> 00:05:26,680
and it's unfair to everyone.

75
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:30,920
How about if

76
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:34,330
the person who finds the jade hairpin

77
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:36,150
gets to be the next city lord?

78
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:49,420
Guys, look over there.

79
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,210
Search carefully.

80
00:05:56,312 --> 00:05:57,800
Have you all seen what happened today?

81
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,710
I heard that man is Xiao Wuxia.

82
00:05:59,770 --> 00:06:00,600
I can't believe it.

83
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,120
Otherwise,

84
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:03,384
why would Elder Ping and Elder Ji

85
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:05,190
be so desperate to capture him?

86
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:07,070
If that is really Xiao Wuxia,

87
00:06:07,096 --> 00:06:08,420
I will be the first to fight him.

88
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,480
Yes, that's right!

89
00:06:09,912 --> 00:06:11,330
If it weren't for the Xiao family,

90
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:13,480
we wouldn't be suffering today.

91
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:14,680
That Xiao Wuxia

92
00:06:14,808 --> 00:06:16,150
actually has the nerve to come back.

93
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:17,040
Right.

94
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:20,100
Xiao Haitian ruined our family,
our wives and children

95
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,920
were separated.

96
00:06:21,048 --> 00:06:22,950
How many of the tribespeople
have left their homes

97
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:24,190
and died, not leaving a corpse?

98
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:24,650
Right!

99
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:25,710
Why should he, a member of

100
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,150
the Xiao family, survive well? Why?

101
00:06:27,450 --> 00:06:27,860
Yes!

102
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:28,860
Right!

103
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,420
Xiao Haitian died just like that,

104
00:06:30,456 --> 00:06:31,510
and it was too easy for him!

105
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:32,770
- Too easy!
- Exactly!

106
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,450
Let's go to the Xiao family now

107
00:06:34,540 --> 00:06:35,360
to get justice!

108
00:06:35,650 --> 00:06:36,360
- Let's go!
- Yes!

109
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:41,010
- Go!
- Go!

110
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,360
Let's go together!

111
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,070
Go!

112
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,390
Let's follow them! Yes!

113
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,360
We'll tear the house down!

114
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:56,630
(Xiao Residence)

115
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,950
(Xiao Residence)

116
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:07,710
(Xiao Residence)

117
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,210
What are you doing here?

118
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:12,504
The Xiao family is right in front.

119
00:07:12,536 --> 00:07:13,120
Smash it!

120
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,944
Go!

121
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:14,888
Make them suffer!

122
00:07:14,888 --> 00:07:15,940
Destroy the Xiao family!

123
00:07:18,810 --> 00:07:20,010
Avenge our loved ones!

124
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,100
Yes, destroy them!

125
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:23,304
This way, it's right in front!

126
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:24,180
Right here!

127
00:07:25,940 --> 00:07:26,500
This way!

128
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:29,010
(Xiao Residence)

129
00:07:34,770 --> 00:07:35,690
Destroy their house!

130
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:53,830
Smash it!

131
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,450
Destroy the Xiao family!

132
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,750
Destroy them! Here!

133
00:08:00,650 --> 00:08:01,540
Here, too!

134
00:08:02,088 --> 00:08:03,770
Don't think you'll have it easy either!

135
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:07,600
Smash it!

136
00:08:10,210 --> 00:08:11,100
Smash it!

137
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:13,690
Here!

138
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,810
Smash it!

139
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,180
Why are they doing this again?

140
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,620
Stop!

141
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:27,060
Stop at once!

142
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:28,380
Harder!

143
00:08:28,570 --> 00:08:30,130
I said stop! Do you hear me?

144
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:33,050
They are already dead,

145
00:08:33,304 --> 00:08:34,856
yet you're still causing a ruckus here.

146
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,320
Leave, do you hear me?

147
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,670
Let's go!

148
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:47,220
Go!

149
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:27,090
♪The wind sighs
as catkins fill the city♪

150
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:31,410
♪The cuckoo cries
as it longs for home♪

151
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,790
Go.

152
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:39,790
Sing me a song.

153
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,144
What song do you want to listen to?

154
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:43,100
I'd like to listen to

155
00:09:43,528 --> 00:09:44,488
Yueluo Ballad.

156
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:49,910
♪The long goose has nowhere to land♪

157
00:09:50,608 --> 00:09:54,830
♪Drinking with the moon
with a cup of sorrow♪

158
00:09:54,910 --> 00:10:00,130
♪Lost in a drunken slumber
before the third watch♪

159
00:10:01,690 --> 00:10:04,590
♪Every night and day♪

160
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:07,350
♪I can only turn my endless yearning♪

161
00:10:07,470 --> 00:10:10,990
♪Into countless stars across the sky♪

162
00:10:10,990 --> 00:10:11,688
(Xiao Residence)

163
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,510
♪Can you see♪

164
00:10:13,570 --> 00:10:15,870
♪My distant homeland♪

165
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:19,670
♪Teary eyes that are shining for you♪

166
00:10:20,110 --> 00:10:22,390
♪Flipping through
those unforgettable scenes♪

167
00:10:22,610 --> 00:10:26,010
♪In my dreams♪

168
00:10:26,090 --> 00:10:29,070
♪It has turned into smoke
in the blink of an eye♪

169
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:33,430
♪Only one song is left in my ear♪

170
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:38,910
♪Singing the ancient fable♪

171
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:45,570
♪The moon is clear
as the moonlight shines bright♪

172
00:10:45,810 --> 00:10:49,430
♪Bright in the sky,
rippling in the water♪

173
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:54,610
♪The place where the moon sets♪

174
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:58,950
♪Must be where home is♪

175
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:01,950
♪Whenever I gaze at the horizon♪

176
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:04,990
♪And the lonely phases of the moon♪

177
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:08,310
♪Past events resurfaced again♪

178
00:11:09,008 --> 00:11:11,270
♪Can you see♪

179
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,710
♪My distant homeland♪

180
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:19,210
♪Beneath the same moon♪

181
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:24,650
♪The moon is clear
as the moonlight shines bright♪

182
00:11:25,050 --> 00:11:28,610
♪As people laugh, their shadows grow♪

183
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:33,670
♪The moonlight makes no sound♪

184
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:38,970
♪A tinkling in my heart♪

185
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:41,790
When I was young,

186
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,380
my master measured my height
like this, too.

187
00:11:53,656 --> 00:11:55,480
The one on the left
belongs to my sister,

188
00:11:56,010 --> 00:11:57,100
and the right one is mine.

189
00:11:59,170 --> 00:12:00,170
In the past,

190
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:02,030
our parents measured our heights

191
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:04,580
every birthday.

192
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,240
I told my sister

193
00:12:11,896 --> 00:12:12,936
that I would grow taller

194
00:12:13,048 --> 00:12:14,580
than her in the next year
every time.

195
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:17,960
I will measure it for you this time.

196
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:57,930
There.

197
00:14:04,648 --> 00:14:05,592
Raise it higher.

198
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,510
Father,

199
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:11,650
did I practice well?

200
00:14:12,504 --> 00:14:14,088
Why do you want to
practice martial arts?

201
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,320
I want to be as brave, strong,

202
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:18,504
(and be a hero that everyone admires,
just like you.)

203
00:14:20,050 --> 00:14:20,580
(Good.)

204
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,528
(Keep going.)

205
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,720
(It's time to eat.)

206
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:26,460
Brother,

207
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:27,240
come on.

208
00:14:27,304 --> 00:14:28,776
It's your favourite Bitterless Congee.

209
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,480
Coming.

210
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:32,550
Are you hungry?

211
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,220
Let's eat.

212
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:35,460
Sure.

213
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:37,840
Watch out.

214
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:05,460
I have made you suffer

215
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,860
yesterday.

216
00:15:07,816 --> 00:15:09,930
Relying solely on a vote
or the martial competition,

217
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:13,130
no elders can secure
the position of city lord,

218
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:17,720
hence they muddled the situation of
the election with the jade hairpin.

219
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,820
The spy, in a rush

220
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,320
to seize the opportunity,

221
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,272
is likely to reveal his true intention.

222
00:15:24,430 --> 00:15:27,080
I'm just concerned that he might
ask for help from Lu Yu.

223
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:28,930
If that happens,

224
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:31,650
I'm afraid your identity may be exposed.

225
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:34,150
You'd better leave as soon as possible.

226
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:37,720
Nothing can be accomplished
without taking risks.

227
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:39,630
I will act with caution discreetly,

228
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:41,930
I will leave as soon as I found the spy.

229
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:43,000
As for the rest,

230
00:15:43,410 --> 00:15:44,650
you can handle it.

231
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:47,770
That works, too.

232
00:15:49,810 --> 00:15:50,750
(Yueluo)

233
00:15:54,550 --> 00:15:55,710
(Liangzhou)

234
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:02,760
According to a confidential report
from Qingkang,

235
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:05,650
Pei Yan has persuaded His Majesty
to implement military reform.

236
00:16:05,768 --> 00:16:07,784
He'll arrive in Liangzhou
in the next few days.

237
00:16:07,930 --> 00:16:09,200
I fear it will endanger you

238
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,930
at that time.

239
00:16:11,010 --> 00:16:12,620
Pei Yan is a little too inexperienced

240
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,580
to deal with me.

241
00:16:16,472 --> 00:16:17,432
My Lord, a letter

242
00:16:17,976 --> 00:16:19,670
from our covert arrangement
in Yueluo came.

243
00:16:19,688 --> 00:16:21,608
The selection of the city lord
has been postponed.

244
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,380
Why?

245
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,960
Someone showed up in Yueluo

246
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:25,740
with a jade hairpin

247
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,720
and disrupted the plan.

248
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:28,790
What jade hairpin?

249
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,504
It is a symbol of Yueluo,

250
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:32,030
also a relic of Xiao Haitian.

251
00:16:32,232 --> 00:16:34,670
Our covert arrangement is speculating
that the man who came

252
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,024
was Xiao Wuxia, Xiao Haitian's son.

253
00:16:36,024 --> 00:16:37,784
I wonder if
there is some kind of conspiracy.

254
00:16:41,650 --> 00:16:42,620
As expected,

255
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:45,740
the slave tribe is timid
and afraid of getting into trouble.

256
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:49,340
Let's not talk about how Xiao Wuxia,

257
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:51,290
a mere lost boy from a doomed family,

258
00:16:51,290 --> 00:16:52,880
could stir up any waves.

259
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:54,840
He's just a dog after all.

260
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,820
Tell him

261
00:16:56,130 --> 00:16:57,670
that the most important thing now is

262
00:16:57,832 --> 00:17:00,056
to take the position of city lord
as soon as possible.

263
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:01,980
Yes, My Lord.

264
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,352
I'll convey the message right away.

265
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:08,610
(Liangzhou)

266
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,620
We are arriving at Zhenyuan Army Camp.

267
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:25,528
I'm afraid General Gong
has set something up.

268
00:17:25,896 --> 00:17:27,320
Your Lordship, you must be careful.

269
00:17:28,936 --> 00:17:31,416
Since the proposal for military reform
has been put forward,

270
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:33,060
it is bound to offend Lu Yu.

271
00:17:34,020 --> 00:17:35,520
I'm afraid it won't be easy

272
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,730
to take Lu Yu back to Qingkang.

273
00:17:38,970 --> 00:17:40,630
We need to

274
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:42,800
divert his attention from me.

275
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:46,190
Have the advance scouts in Liangzhou

276
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,779
found any leads
on Wei Zhao's whereabouts?

277
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:48,360
There is none.

278
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:50,410
Could it be

279
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,040
that he is not in Liangzhou?

280
00:17:57,260 --> 00:17:59,730
Liangzhou is adjacent to Yueluo.

281
