to bring Lu Yu back,

302
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:52,490
both are beneficial to me.

303
00:18:52,696 --> 00:18:54,296
This is killing two birds
with one stone.

304
00:18:54,296 --> 00:18:55,592
Your Lordship, that's brilliant.

305
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:09,770
(Liangzhou)

306
00:19:29,170 --> 00:19:29,880
How do you

307
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,600
have no sense of
mutual understanding at all?

308
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,609
Where was this night owl
from, disturbing

309
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:36,150
