313
00:19:51,490 --> 00:19:53,340
Nice things are mysterious.

314
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:05,800
Alright.

315
00:20:22,730 --> 00:20:23,150
Let's go.

316
00:20:24,930 --> 00:20:25,768
Watch out for steps.

317
00:21:05,390 --> 00:21:05,880
We're here.

318
00:21:07,620 --> 00:21:08,670
You may take that off.

319
00:21:33,090 --> 00:21:37,350
