and seeing everything red♪

326
00:22:07,670 --> 00:22:08,560
Are you crying?

327
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:10,930
No.

328
00:22:10,970 --> 00:22:11,650
Let me see.

329
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:13,840
No.

330
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,100
I don't believe you, let me see.

331
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:15,990
I'm really not.

332
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:17,060
Show me.

333
00:22:17,170 --> 00:22:18,360
I said no.

334
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:25,300
I won't stare at you,

335
00:22:25,990 --> 00:22:26,792
I'll just push you.

336
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:34,650
