I suddenly look back♪

337
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:39,010
♪The face that feels so dear to me♪

338
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:43,330
♪Where are you now?♪

339
00:22:48,270 --> 00:22:52,550
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

340
00:22:52,670 --> 00:22:56,930
♪Looking back, it seems like a dream♪

341
