even if we're far apart♪

342
00:23:01,670 --> 00:23:06,050
♪Don't waste time♪

343
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:10,490
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

344
00:23:10,630 --> 00:23:15,030
