in a flash♪

345
00:23:16,280 --> 00:23:17,080
Shameless Cat,

346
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:20,170
just do

347
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,560
whatever you want to.

348
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,300
It's your turn to push me now.

349
00:23:52,910 --> 00:23:53,910
Where are you going?

350
00:23:54,730 --> 00:23:55,910
Didn't you say

351
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:57,320
that I can just do

352
00:23:57,650 --> 00:23:58,540
whatever I want to?

353
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:28,820
Hello.

354
00:24:29,130 --> 00:24:29,760
Have you seen

355
00:24:29,760 --> 00:24:31,450
a Liangzhou woman in her forties?

356
00:24:31,780 --> 00:24:32,600
- No.
- Hi,

357
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,320
have you met a woman

358
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:33,940
with curved brows?

359
00:24:33,942 --> 00:24:34,800
Hi, have you seen

360
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,080
