363
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:38,820
Hello,

364
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:39,992
have you seen a Liangzhou woman

365
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,670
in her forties?

366
00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:42,410
Hello, may I ask if you met this person?

367
00:24:42,456 --> 00:24:43,170
