371
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:47,600
No.

372
00:24:47,710 --> 00:24:48,710
Hi, have you seen

373
00:24:48,710 --> 00:24:50,300
a woman with thin and curved brows?

374
00:24:50,820 --> 00:24:51,380
No.

375
00:24:51,690 --> 00:24:52,990
This is a very important letter.

376
00:24:52,990 --> 00:24:54,650
Please be sure
to send it to Jiang Village.

377
00:24:56,380 --> 00:24:57,230
Don't worry, Miss.

378
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,520
Thank you.

379
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:00,150
Jiang Ci, let's go.

380
00:25:01,650 --> 00:25:03,670
Why did you think of
writing a letter to your master?

381
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:06,080
What if I get sidetracked from her?

382
00:25:06,230 --> 00:25:07,670
I'm sending a letter back

383
00:25:07,710 --> 00:25:08,990
just in case.

384
00:25:09,410 --> 00:25:11,630
She won't worry if she knows I'm safe.

385
00:25:13,690 --> 00:25:14,230
Let's go.

386
00:25:14,360 --> 00:25:14,880
Keep looking.

387
00:25:25,490 --> 00:25:26,080
Sir,

388
00:25:26,470 --> 00:25:28,080
we might as well prepare two plans

389
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,840
and use that girl's name

390
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,080
to draw the Yans out.

391
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:32,340
Amidst the chaos,

392
00:25:32,560 --> 00:25:33,780
we can also escape.

393
00:25:33,910 --> 00:25:34,520
No,

394
00:25:36,630 --> 00:25:37,760
we have to do them one by one.

395
00:25:38,650 --> 00:25:39,470
Lure the spy first.

396
00:25:41,990 --> 00:25:42,430
Noted.

397
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:01,170
What's wrong?

398
00:26:01,490 --> 00:26:02,170
Nothing.

399
00:26:02,730 --> 00:26:04,210
I just went out for a walk.

400
00:26:07,230 --> 00:26:09,450
My master must be
looking for me everywhere now.

401
00:26:09,950 --> 00:26:11,280
It's getting colder,

402
00:26:11,670 --> 00:26:13,450
if her leg's condition attacks again,

403
00:26:13,580 --> 00:26:15,272
there will be no one
to give her a massage.

404
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:19,130
Come,

405
00:26:19,710 --> 00:26:20,730
I'll take you somewhere.

406
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:28,560
Sir, can I have your order?

407
00:26:29,300 --> 00:26:31,150
Get us all your signature dishes.

408
00:26:31,580 --> 00:26:32,744
He is not short of money.

409
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:33,840
Sure.

410
00:26:34,370 --> 00:26:36,056
Two servings
of Bitterless Congee, please.

411
00:26:37,950 --> 00:26:39,600
Are you not from Yueluo?

412
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:41,450
We are,

413
00:26:41,544 --> 00:26:42,860
but we just came back recently.

414
00:26:43,864 --> 00:26:45,430
We don't serve Bitterless Congee here.

415
00:26:45,690 --> 00:26:46,650
Why not?

416
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:48,040
No means no.

417
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:49,120
Just order something else

418
00:26:49,210 --> 00:26:50,170
or leave now.

419
00:26:50,360 --> 00:26:51,496
Stop disrupting my business.

420
00:26:52,130 --> 00:26:54,080
We'll have eggs instead, then.

421
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:56,760
Forget it,

422
00:26:57,064 --> 00:26:58,120
let's go to another place.

423
00:26:59,670 --> 00:27:00,520
Go, then.

424
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:02,410
We don't sell Bitterless Congee here.

425
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:11,260
Yueluo is huge,

426
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:13,060
why isn't Bitterless Congee available?

427
00:27:15,670 --> 00:27:17,380
It's fine, let's go get something else.

428
00:27:18,744 --> 00:27:20,130
Lingjiu Flower is in Mingyue Valley,

429
00:27:20,408 --> 00:27:21,410
I'll take you to find it.

430
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:28,280
This is exactly the same as what

431
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:29,352
was written in Yueluo Guide.

432
00:27:30,504 --> 00:27:31,890
Mingyue Valley is right in front.

433
00:28:12,260 --> 00:28:12,904
What's wrong?

434
00:28:13,690 --> 00:28:14,970
I have a stomach ache.

435
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,600
We should go back first.

436
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:19,230
Let's go.

437
00:28:26,620 --> 00:28:27,950
Mountains and rivers of Zhenyuan

438
00:28:28,020 --> 00:28:29,300
and Ningbian endure forever!

439
00:28:29,380 --> 00:28:30,650
Mountains and rivers of Zhenyuan

440
00:28:30,710 --> 00:28:31,990
and Ningbian endure forever!

