00:28:32,130 --> 00:28:33,410
Mountains and rivers of Zhenyuan

442
00:28:33,470 --> 00:28:34,760
and Ningbian endure forever!

443
00:28:53,890 --> 00:28:56,320
Greetings, General Lu.

444
00:28:57,384 --> 00:28:59,448
I have heard about Zhenyuan Army
for a long time.

445
00:28:59,730 --> 00:29:00,430
Seeing it today,

446
00:29:00,990 --> 00:29:02,360
it truly exudes an impressive aura.

447
00:29:04,690 --> 00:29:05,410
Pei Yan,

448
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:07,280
I know very well the reason

449
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:10,730
you came here this time.

450
00:29:10,840 --> 00:29:12,760
I came here because of
the military reform.

451
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:16,880
Your memorial

452
00:29:17,260 --> 00:29:20,780
is aimed at handing over
my Zhenyuan army to others.

453
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,760
General Lu, you are right.

454
00:29:23,010 --> 00:29:25,112
After the reform, the deployment
of troops and allocation

455
00:29:25,128 --> 00:29:27,130
of salaries will follow
the unified planning of the court.

456
00:29:27,130 --> 00:29:28,430
That depends on the rules

457
00:29:28,860 --> 00:29:29,950
and the current situation.

458
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:33,540
Rules are set by His Majesty,

459
00:29:33,580 --> 00:29:36,650
and the situation is made by people.

460
00:29:40,910 --> 00:29:41,520
Pei Yan,

461
00:29:41,890 --> 00:29:43,730
you handed me the account book earlier

462
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:46,710
and you are now taking control
of the military reform.

463
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:51,620
You have repeatedly
caused issues for me.

464
00:29:52,730 --> 00:29:55,040
Aren't you afraid that I might kill you?

465
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:57,760
I feel ashamed regarding the matter
of the account book.

466
00:29:58,300 --> 00:30:00,860
I will certainly apologize to you.

467
00:30:00,950 --> 00:30:02,730
How about I prepare a feast

468
00:30:02,910 --> 00:30:05,190
and invite Sanlang, too?

469
00:30:05,912 --> 00:30:07,912
General Lu, I kindly ask for
your participation.

470
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:10,710
Is Wei Zhao

471
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,380
in Liangzhou, too?

472
00:30:15,910 --> 00:30:17,880
Hasn't Sanlang come to visit?

473
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:21,970
There must be some delays.

474
00:30:29,210 --> 00:30:31,080
What are all of you doing?

475
00:30:31,256 --> 00:30:32,540
Wei Zhao is here in Liangzhou,

476
00:30:32,630 --> 00:30:33,840
yet none of you knows?

477
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,376
General Lu, please calm down.

478
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:39,930
Wei Zhao must have come to
investigate me on the orders of Xie Che.

479
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:42,210
Get your men to be more alert.

480
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:44,104
Lead a team to search for
Wei Zhao's whereabouts

481
00:30:44,104 --> 00:30:46,580
both inside and outside the city.

482
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,320
Yes, General.

483
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:49,240
Get lost.

484
00:30:52,340 --> 00:30:53,800
Everything was as expected by Lord Pei.

485
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:55,576
General Lu has his attention set
on Wei Zhao.

486
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:56,580
Send someone to Yueluo

487
00:30:56,776 --> 00:30:58,319
to find out Wei Zhao's whereabouts.

488
00:30:58,320 --> 00:30:59,000
Yes, Your Lordship.

489
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:01,210
Remember to look for Ci, too.

490
00:31:02,008 --> 00:31:03,080
Bring her back immediately

491
00:31:03,540 --> 00:31:04,430
if you find her.

492
00:31:05,912 --> 00:31:06,840
Yes, Your Lordship.

493
00:31:06,888 --> 00:31:07,340
Remember,

494
00:31:08,580 --> 00:31:09,950
never ever hurt her.

495
00:31:47,970 --> 00:31:49,130
Is your stomach still hurting?

496
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:52,060
No.

497
00:31:53,450 --> 00:31:53,800
Let's go,

498
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,864
I'll take you to find Lingjiu Flower.

499
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:57,970
It's fine.

500
00:31:58,360 --> 00:31:59,760
I'm not in a rush anyway.

501
00:32:00,130 --> 00:32:01,730
Haven't you been very busy recently?

502
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:03,840
Let's search for them again

503
00:32:03,976 --> 00:32:05,080
when you're less occupied.

504
00:32:08,360 --> 00:32:08,840
Fine.

505
00:32:36,950 --> 00:32:37,670
Yu Lian,

506
00:32:38,630 --> 00:32:40,230
I'd like to ask about Mingyue Valley.

507
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:42,490
You have seen it.

508
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:04,100
(With the ongoing war,)

509
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:06,744
(Yueluo is trapped between
Liang and Wei State,)

510
00:33:06,776 --> 00:33:08,130
(caught in a precarious situation.)

511
00:33:10,360 --> 00:33:12,490
(Coupled with Lu Yu's
rampant slaughter,)

512
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:16,380
(Mingyue Valley has already become
a mass grave.)

513
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:19,990
(No Lingjiu Flowers)

514
00:33:20,560 --> 00:33:22,580
(can be grown on mass graves.)

515
00:33:23,496 --> 00:33:24,470
(Hence, Bitterless Congee)

516
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:27,450
(has extinct.)

517
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:37,670
Father.

518
00:33:38,760 --> 00:33:39,230
Mother.

519
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:40,890
Xiu.

520
00:33:41,670 --> 00:33:42,300
Ying.

521
00:33:43,170 --> 00:33:44,360
I'm here to see you.

522
00:33:44,690 --> 00:33:46,600
I've been well.

523
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,190
Do not worry about me

524
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:50,580
down there.

525
00:33:52,450 --> 00:33:53,840
I miss you so much.

526
00:34:34,210 --> 00:34:38,430
♪The moon is clear
as the moonlight shines bright♪

527
00:34:38,690 --> 00:34:42,290
♪Bright in the sky,
rippling in the water♪

528
00:34:43,250 --> 00:34:47,470
♪The place where the moon sets♪

529
00:34:47,570 --> 00:34:51,790
♪Must be where home is♪

530
00:35:20,050 --> 00:35:24,290
♪The wind sighs
as catkins fill the city♪

531
00:35:24,370 --> 00:35:28,590
♪The cuckoo cries as it longs for home♪

532
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:33,550
♪Home is nowhere in sight
on the difficult path♪

533
00:35:33,650 --> 00:35:37,890
♪As melancholic as the layers of sand♪

534
00:35:38,410 --> 00:35:42,630
♪The rain pours as if it's weeping♪

535
00:35:42,850 --> 00:35:47,050
♪The long goose has nowhere to land♪

536
00:35:47,790 --> 00:35:52,030
