with a cup of sorrow♪

537
00:35:56,570 --> 00:35:57,660
You saw.

538
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,450
You already found out that day.

539
00:36:02,160 --> 00:36:03,340
Why didn't you let me see it?

540
00:36:04,010 --> 00:36:05,050
My heart feels sorrow when I

541
00:36:05,050 --> 00:36:06,510
see it although I'm just an outsider.

542
00:36:07,140 --> 00:36:07,930
Let alone you.

543
00:36:09,050 --> 00:36:09,740
I...

544
00:36:12,110 --> 00:36:14,570
How do you know I'm not an outsider?

545
00:36:17,290 --> 00:36:19,570
♪Flipping through
those unforgettable scenes♪

546
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:22,240
Yu Lian told me

547
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,260
that Yueluo tolls the bell

548
00:36:24,490 --> 00:36:25,640
every full moon.

549
00:36:27,050 --> 00:36:29,470
It was originally
to commemorate the dead,

550
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,820
but it has now turned into a prayer,

551
00:36:32,152 --> 00:36:34,488
to pray for those who have left home
but have not returned

552
00:36:34,530 --> 00:36:35,550
to be safe and happy.

553
00:36:39,740 --> 00:36:42,510
Yueluo is just a small town

554
00:36:42,950 --> 00:36:44,380
caught between two big states.

555
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:46,910
There is never a choice,

556
00:36:48,010 --> 00:36:50,220
so this is inevitable.

557
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:29,090
I wanted to learn
how to play this for you,

558
00:37:29,740 --> 00:37:31,180
but I've only heard it once.

559
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:54,410
I will find Lingjiu Flowers.

560
00:38:58,180 --> 00:38:59,470
I've already searched for it.

561
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:01,570
It has extinct.

562
00:39:03,390 --> 00:39:05,240
Humans think plants are weak

563
00:39:05,430 --> 00:39:06,680
and can be trampled at will.

564
00:39:07,220 --> 00:39:08,660
However, all plants have souls,

565
00:39:08,904 --> 00:39:10,910
and they have vitality stronger
than that of humans.

566
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:13,160
If Lingjiu Flowers can grow
beside coffins

567
00:39:13,450 --> 00:39:14,510
and survive for years,

568
00:39:14,990 --> 00:39:15,736
I choose to believe

569
00:39:15,736 --> 00:39:17,610
that it won't allow itself
to die so easily.

570
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,450
Even if the flowers are extinct,

571
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:20,840
there will still be seeds.

572
00:39:26,260 --> 00:39:27,410
I won't be here in a few days,

573
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,712
you should follow Yu Lian

574
00:39:28,776 --> 00:39:29,864
instead of running around.

575
00:39:30,030 --> 00:39:31,410
Will you be in danger?

576
00:39:33,220 --> 00:39:34,450
Those who can hurt me...

577
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:50,860
This is for you.

578
00:39:57,030 --> 00:39:58,232
Is this the one that hurt me?

579
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:02,232
Use it for self-defense.

580
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:04,936
I never expected that one day,

581
00:40:05,410 --> 00:40:06,890
the thing that hurt me

582
00:40:07,340 --> 00:40:08,410
could also protect me.

583
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:12,450
The world is unpredictable,

584
00:40:12,504 --> 00:40:14,184
and people's hearts are easily swayed.

585
00:40:15,010 --> 00:40:20,190
♪Let it fly with the wind
into sweet dreams♪

586
00:40:21,490 --> 00:40:23,810
♪The beautiful moments we shared♪

587
00:40:23,890 --> 00:40:29,090
♪Last through time,
we never leave each other♪

588
00:40:32,530 --> 00:40:33,640
I bought it two days ago.

589
00:40:33,930 --> 00:40:34,904
There is not much left.

590
00:40:34,984 --> 00:40:36,248
You should come back early.

591
00:40:36,312 --> 00:40:40,110
♪Your face stays vivid in my mind♪

592
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:40,640
I will.

593
00:40:42,650 --> 00:40:44,870
♪Bound to each other♪

594
00:40:44,930 --> 00:40:49,070
♪Like flowing water,
love and hate continue♪

595
00:40:49,210 --> 00:40:51,430
♪I only wish♪

596
00:40:51,470 --> 00:40:53,710
♪For your unwavering heart♪

597
00:40:56,450 --> 00:40:57,760
(Just do)

598
00:40:57,990 --> 00:40:59,070
(whatever you want to do.)

599
00:41:00,310 --> 00:41:02,550
♪I hold your hands through eternity♪

600
00:41:02,610 --> 00:41:06,770
♪Time cannot separate us♪

601
00:41:06,930 --> 00:41:10,750
♪Our longings go on♪

602
00:41:47,430 --> 00:41:48,180
Young Master,

603
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:50,490
I really can't understand

604
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:52,640
why would you keep the jade hairpin

605
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:54,300
with that girl.

606
00:41:55,910 --> 00:41:57,180
I have to show up in person,

607
00:41:57,656 --> 00:41:59,352
so I can't have
the jade hairpin with me.

608
00:41:59,976 --> 00:42:01,208
I'll let her have it for now.

609
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,340
That is such an important object,

610
00:42:03,384 --> 00:42:04,712
and you're letting her have it?

611
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:06,200
What if she betrays you?

612
00:42:06,260 --> 00:42:07,660
What do we do then?

613
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:10,930
Tell Yu Lian to take care of them,

614
00:42:11,390 --> 00:42:12,780
and don't make any more mistakes.

615
00:42:13,450 --> 00:42:15,140
Stop showing her attitude either.

616
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:22,910
Any news from Qingkang?

617
00:42:24,552 --> 00:42:25,848
Pei Yan submitted a memorial

618
00:42:25,848 --> 00:42:27,860
to His Majesty
regarding the military reform

619
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:30,616
and His Majesty asked him
to head to Liangzhou.

620
00:42:31,070 --> 00:42:32,180
According to this timing,

621
00:42:32,664 --> 00:42:34,168
he should have arrived at Luying.

622
00:42:34,744 --> 00:42:35,760
With him coming like this,

623
00:42:36,648 --> 00:42:38,530
it's hard to guarantee
that he won't interfere

624
00:42:38,530 --> 00:42:39,640
and create complications.

625
00:42:41,740 --> 00:42:43,510
I still have his account book with me,

626
00:42:43,704 --> 00:42:45,656
so he wouldn't dare to
confront me openly for now.

627
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:46,950
Just be cautious.

628
00:42:47,260 --> 00:42:47,820
Yes.

629
00:43:01,930 --> 00:43:02,880
He is gone.

630
00:43:03,640 --> 00:43:05,592
Do you know where can I
find Lingjiu Flowers

631
00:43:05,608 --> 00:43:06,700
other than Mingyue Valley?

632
00:43:07,510 --> 00:43:08,530
Why are you asking this?

633
00:43:10,300 --> 00:43:11,910
I want to grow Lingjiu Flowers.

634
00:43:12,720 --> 00:43:13,570
Very arrogant.

635
00:43:16,340 --> 00:43:17,432
Do you know the answer?

636
00:43:18,430 --> 00:43:19,740
Just tell me.

637
00:43:21,300 --> 00:43:22,780
Just tell her already.

638
00:43:22,860 --> 00:43:25,016
I don't want to be annoyed
to death by her these days.

639
00:43:26,456 --> 00:43:27,752
There's no point telling her.

640
00:43:27,848 --> 00:43:29,688
Mingyue Valley is often blown
by the west wind,

641
00:43:30,010 --> 00:43:31,360
and to the east is Guxing Peak.

642
00:43:32,010 --> 00:43:32,990
There is a possibility

643
00:43:34,470 --> 00:43:35,070
that the seeds

644
00:43:35,070 --> 00:43:36,280
would be blown there.

645
00:43:37,220 --> 00:43:38,920
Guxing Peak's terrain
is steep and perilous,

646
00:43:38,968 --> 00:43:40,312
and you wouldn't be able to hike it.

647
00:43:41,160 --> 00:43:42,792
How do you know that
if I don't try?

648
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:53,180
Are you actually going to show up?

649
00:43:54,240 --> 00:43:56,360
Luring the snake out of its hole
is the fastest way.

650
00:43:56,780 --> 00:43:58,070
That is too dangerous.

651
00:43:58,260 --> 00:44:00,590
I was the one who dragged you
into this in the first place.

652
00:44:00,590 --> 00:44:02,800
If you get exposed because of this,

653
00:44:02,860 --> 00:44:03,490
well...

654
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:06,390
I want all the people
in Yueluo to witness

655
00:44:06,890 --> 00:44:09,890
the day I avenge my father's injustice.

656
00:44:42,704 --> 00:44:47,054
♪The slanting sunray refuses to leave♪

657
00:44:47,314 --> 00:44:50,664
♪The moon is fading off♪

658
00:44:51,634 --> 00:44:55,894
♪Frost on the sword, string of the bow♪

659
00:44:56,194 --> 00:45:00,074
♪Bond people together♪

660
00:45:00,644 --> 00:45:04,864
♪The rain heading north and
the wild geese returning from the south♪

661
00:45:04,864 --> 00:45:08,874
♪Who can meet again?♪

662
00:45:09,434 --> 00:45:13,384
♪Looking at the mountains far away
and seeing everything red♪

663
00:45:13,384 --> 00:45:17,624
♪Immersed in the passing years♪

664
00:45:17,854 --> 00:45:22,274
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

665
00:45:22,274 --> 00:45:26,164
♪Yet now I am left wandering
in this life♪

666
00:45:26,734 --> 00:45:30,854
♪Faint memories of the past♪

667
00:45:31,074 --> 00:45:34,924
♪All tell of parting sorrows♪

668
00:45:35,604 --> 00:45:39,844
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

669
00:45:40,084 --> 00:45:44,014
♪Amidst the wind, I suddenly look back♪

670
00:45:44,464 --> 00:45:48,454
♪The face that feels so dear to me♪

671
00:45:48,834 --> 00:45:52,274
♪Where are you now?♪

672
00:45:57,804 --> 00:46:02,194
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

673
00:46:02,194 --> 00:46:06,034
♪Looking back, it seems like a dream♪

674
00:46:06,554 --> 00:46:10,804
♪Don’t forget each other
even if we're far apart♪

675
00:46:11,184 --> 00:46:14,864
♪Don't waste time♪

676
00:46:15,554 --> 00:46:19,744
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

677
00:46:20,014 --> 00:46:23,884
♪Taste all the vicissitudes of life
in a flash♪

678
00:46:24,494 --> 00:46:28,634
♪Though nothing is permanent♪

679
00:46:29,214 --> 00:46:32,664
♪I wish you well♪
